                                           |
                                           v
+-----------------------------+     +-----------------------------+
| Rust-based Response Engine | --> | Flutter or React Dashboard  |
| (blocks/quarantines/alerts)|     | (analytics + forensics view)|
+-----------------------------+     +-----------------------------+


